Package com.app.numbers.sort

Interface Sort<T extends Comparable<T>>

Type Parameters:
T - The type of elements to be sorted. It must implement Comparable<T extends Comparable<T>> for comparisons.
All Known Implementing Classes:
BubbleSort, InsertSort, MergeSort, QuickSort, SelectSort
public interface Sort<T extends Comparable<T>>
The Sort interface defines methods for sorting lists of elements. Implementations of this interface should provide concrete sorting algorithms.

      Sorts the provided list using the specified comparator.
      Parameters:
      arr - The list of elements to be sorted. Must not be null or empty.
